        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 7 at 12:03PM MDT until August 8 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...High temperatures up to 107 degrees are expected.

* WHERE...Crowley, Otero, Bent, and Prowers.

* WHEN...For the first Heat Advisory, until 8 PM MDT this evening.
For the second Heat Advisory, from 11 AM to 8 PM MDT Friday.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures  may cause heat illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
